{"tid":682443,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬喉舌報導 C朗續約跳草裙舞已經觸怒皇馬高層","createTime":"2018-05-29T01:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T03:02:21.000Z","uid":54373,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"25c5f4daebb2be380075f3a67f5ee66969d72daa","tid":682443,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T01:20:28.000Z","msg":"皇馬歐聯捧盃兼3連冠應該高高興興，點知就畀C朗一個搞到掃晒慶，佢由基輔賽後到返回馬德里，不停咁話要未來一周決定自己前途，唔肯收口，直情係搞寸晒皇馬個Party，西媒爆料，C朗呢啲行為觸怒晒皇馬上下，搞到大家關係非常緊張。 <br />\n<br />\n《馬卡報》報道，C朗扭計行為可謂不識大體，隊中好多球員都認為，續唔續約呢啲問題，實在唔適宜喺呢啲喜慶場合討論，遲啲傾都未遲，而皇馬高層班老人家亦有傳開始對C朗不滿。 <br />\n<br />\n連球迷都覺得C朗做錯咗，有民意調查顯示，8成網民都認為C朗喺呢個時候扭計係不合時宜，連民意都幫皇馬，呢壇C朗跳草裙舞鬧劇，到底幾時落幕？"},{"pid":"c503a72d9a0a8bee5641e25b51b6eaed3e005f88","tid":682443,"uid":19126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T01:24:53.000Z","msg":"皇馬廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e6059c067c428f8e9204481c668a18bbaf6b072","tid":682443,"uid":179467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T01:26:07.000Z","msg":"C朗go back to Man U la diu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c1274ca59c479017794311a0aece6085bb61de","tid":682443,"uid":30040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T01:27:12.000Z","msg":"皇馬幫佢交左份稅項罰單，牙朗咪收口囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce9c57b35a9f9fd3652d10b7f4cab7ab2cf3a7d","tid":682443,"uid":45817,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"決賽入唔到波冇得show 肌<br />\n係要9 up 下搶返焦點"},{"pid":"146c5aae5575eb5c6e6d7fb6de87b691644a1540","tid":682443,"uid":27882,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T01:29:52.000Z","msg":"多謝王騎每日9點開始就幫手報導c朗新聞,等我唔使上網周圍搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e187852198c6939d1ccc83efa5d0bd786cfc2c0a","tid":682443,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"146c5a